snippet.title: Ripple Effect Trailer
snippet.description:
Ripple Effect is a free VR gaming platform (for the HTC VIVE/Oculus Rift) set in a variety of different environments in which you travel through portals to play a series of single- and multiplayer minigames.  With free weekly updates, players will unlock new worlds that will expand the game’s virtual universe. 

Ripple Effect is set to launch at the end of May 2017

http://www.wellplayedstudios.com/

contact@wellplayedstudios.com
